data.description: Located in a desirable area of Port Charlotte, this fabulous pool home has a lot to offer and features a metal roof, hurricane shutters all around, cozy feel, large pool with spa and fenced backyard with doggie doors in place from the home and lanai for your ease. The exterior front entry of the home is screened and covered and as you enter the home you walk into the inviting living room that is open to the dining room with access to the large lanai and kitchen with copper metal backsplash, granite countertops, pantry and conveniently located for entertaining! Living space has bamboo flooring and the home also offers a split bedroom floor plan with large guest bedrooms that have tile flooring. The master bedroom with guest bath and large walk-in closet has gorgeous slate floors that also lead into the spacious laundry room. The lanai, pool and spa are the perfect place to enjoy the Florida weather or your family and friends while overlooking the private backyard. A must see to appreciate. Call today for an appointment to see your new home!
